        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>International Spending Transparency Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of State to establish the Unit to Audit US Contributions to Multilateral and International Organizations to audit and report on the contributions to those organizations during the preceding fiscal year.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
